{"title_page": "List of adaptations of works by Stephen King", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=April 2015}}\nThis is a list of media based on work by [[Stephen King]] (including the [[Richard Bachman]] titles). Note that aside from ''[[Creepshow 2]]'', ''[[It Chapter Two]]'', and ''[[Doctor Sleep (2019 film)|Doctor Sleep]]'', the sequels are only tangentially related to Stephen King's work.\n\n==Films==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=\"100%\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Films\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Director\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Distributor\n! [[Rotten Tomatoes|RT]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{sort|1970|1970s}}\n|-\n| 1976\n| ''[[Carrie (1976 film)|Carrie]]''\n| [[Brian De Palma]]\n| [[Carrie (novel)|Based on the novel of the same name]]. \n| [[United Artists]]\n| 92%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1003625_carrie?|title=Carrie (1976)|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango Media]]|accessdate=November 4, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{sort|1980|1980s}}\n|-\n| 1980\n| {{sort|Shining|''[[The Shining (film)|The Shining]]''}}\n| [[Stanley Kubrick]]\n| [[The Shining (novel)|Based on the novel of the same name]]. \n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Warner Bros.]]\n| 85%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shining|title=The Shining (1980)|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango Media]]|accessdate=April 5, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Creepshow]]''\n| [[George A. Romero]]\n| Based on the short stories \"[[Weeds (short story)|Weeds]]\" and \"[[The Crate]]\", the rest is original work for the film. \n| 73%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/creepshow/|title=Creepshow (1982)|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=November 4, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 1983\n| ''[[Cujo (film)|Cujo]]''\n| [[Lewis Teague]]\n| [[Cujo|Based on the novel of the same name]]. \n| 61%<ref>{{cite web|tit