omatoes.com/m/geralds_game |title=Gerald's Game (2017) |publisher=[[Fandango Media]]|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=September 19, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[1922 (2017 film)|1922]]''\n| [[Zak Hilditch]]\n| [[1922 (novella)|Based on the novella of the same name]]. \n| 90%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1922_2017/|title=1922 (2017)|website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango Media]]|accessdate=November 4, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2019\n| ''[[Pet Sematary (2019 film)|Pet Sematary]]''\n| Kevin K\u00f6lsch<br />Dennis Widmyer\n| Based on the novel of the same name. \n| Paramount Pictures\n| 57%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pet_sematary_2019 |title=Pet Semetary (2019)|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango Media]]|accessdate=November 4, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[It Chapter Two]]''\n| Andy Muschietti\n| Based on the novel of the same name. \n| Warner Bros.\n| 63%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/it_chapter_two|title=It Chapter Two (2019)|website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango Media]]|accessdate=October 9, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[In the Tall Grass (film)|In the Tall Grass]]''\n| [[Vincenzo Natali]]\n| [[In the Tall Grass|Based on the novella of the same name]], co-authored with his son, [[Joe Hill (writer)|Joe Hill]]. \n| Netflix\n| 38%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://rottentomatoes.com/m/in_the_tall_grass_2019|title=In the Tall Grass (2019)|website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango Media]]|accessdate=November 4, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Doctor Sleep (2019 film)|Doctor Sleep]]''\n| Mike Flanagan\n| [[Doctor Sleep (novel)|Based on the novel of the same name]].\n| Warner Bros.\n| 77%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/doctor_sleep/|title=Doctor Sleep (2019)|website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango Media]]|access-date=November 12, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{sort|3000|Upcoming films}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"10\" |TBA\n|{{so