y|Misery}}</ref>\n|-\n| 1992\n| {{sort|Lawnmower Man|''[[The Lawnmower Man (film)|The Lawnmower Man]]''}}\n| [[Brett Leonard]]\n| [[The Lawnmower Man|Based on the novel of the same name]]. \n| [[New Line Cinema]]\n| 35%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lawnmower_man|title=The Lawnmower Man (1992)|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=May 6, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1993\n| {{sort|Dark Half|''[[The Dark Half (film)|The Dark Half]]''}}\n| George A. Romero\n| [[The Dark Half|Based on the novel of the same name]].\n| [[Orion Pictures]]\n| 56%<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dark_half/| title=The Dark Half (1993) | publisher=[[Fandango Media]] |work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate=November 4, 2019}}</ref> \n|-\n| ''[[Needful Things (film)|Needful Things]]''\n| [[Fraser Clarke Heston]]\n| [[Needful Things|Based on the novel of the same name]].\n| rowspan=\"2\" | Columbia Pictures\n| 31%<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/needful_things/ | title=Needful Things (1993) | publisher=[[Fandango Media]] |work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate=November 4, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 1994\n| {{sort|Shawshank Redemption|''[[The Shawshank Redemption]]''}}\n| [[Frank Darabont]]\n| Based on the novella \"[[Rita Hayworth and Shawshank Redemption]]\". \n| 90%<ref>{{cite web |title=The Shawshank Redemption (1994) |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shawshank_redemption/ |work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=September 18, 2017 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20170918210429/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shawshank_redemption/ |archivedate=September 18, 2017 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1995\n| {{sort|Mangler|''[[The Mangler (film)|The Mangler]]''}}\n| [[Tobe Hooper]]\n| [[The Mangler|Based on the short story of the same name]]. \n| New Line Cinema\n| 27%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mangler/|title=The Mangler (1995)|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=20 January 2014}}</ref>\n